sentences.text:
Orrcon has incurred additional costs of AUD2,682,453.14 comprising:
 (a) testing costs of AUD1,297,770.02;
 (b) handling costs of AUD647,807.54;
 (c) transportation costs of AUD657,134.70;
 (d) travelling costs of AUD79,740.88.

The way forward as I see it is:


 &#61863; If there is acceptance that Capital Steel/Dongbu will extend the payment terms for shipments 1, 2 and 3 from 120 to 180 days;
 &#61863; Additionally there is acceptance that Capital Steel/Dongbu will pay to Orrcon, all costs associated with sample cutting, testing, handling and transport, stockpiling, de-metring and end reparation.
